'''2020年布基納法索大選'''於2020年11月22日（星期日）舉行，選出新一屆[[布吉納法索|布基納法索]]總統和[[国民议会_(布基纳法索)|国民议会]]議員。<ref name=voa01>{{Cite news |url=https://www.voanews.com/africa/polls-close-burkina-faso-elections |title=Polls Close in Burkina Faso Elections |publisher=VOA |date=2020-11-22 |accessdate=2020-11-24 |archive-date=2020-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130083202/https://www.voanews.com/africa/polls-close-burkina-faso-elections |dead-url=no }}</ref>

全國獨立選舉委員會表示有大量選民因北部和東部的暴力威脅而無法投票。<ref name=voa01/><ref name=bbc01>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-55014928 |title=Burkina Faso election takes place amid jihadist threat |publisher=BBC |date=2020-11-22 |accessdate=2020-11-24 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202092259/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-55014928 |dead-url=no }}</ref>超過900個投票站未有在投票日開放，近60萬名選民受影響。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/africa/burkina-faso-president-roch-marc-christian-kabore-re-elected/2020/11/26/1f727c58-2ff0-11eb-9dd6-2d0179981719_story.html |title=Burkina Faso president Roch Marc Christian Kabore re-elected |publisher=The Washington Post |date=2020-11-26 |accessdate=2020-12-01 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202181831/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/africa/burkina-faso-president-roch-marc-christian-kabore-re-elected/2020/11/26/1f727c58-2ff0-11eb-9dd6-2d0179981719_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==選舉制度==
總統選舉採用[[兩輪選舉制|兩輪選舉制]]。<ref>[http://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/2501/ Burkina Faso: Election for President] {{Wayback|url=http://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/2501/ |date=20201128155310 }} IFES</ref>

國民議會選舉採用[[比例代表制|比例代表制]]，111席由45個多議席選區選出，每區有2至9席，16席由一個全國性選區選出，合計127席。<ref>[http://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/2819/ Burkina Faso: Election for Assemblée Nationale (Burkinabe National Assembly)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/2819/ |date=20201211192202 }} IFES</ref>

